data.description: Let's make a deal! Step into the future to your dream home! Sellers are offering $10,000 in closing credit or interest rate buy down!This well maintained and recently painted home sits on a one acre corner lot a little bit up from the road giving you lots of privacy and distant views. The kitchen is nice and bright, it has recently been upgraded with kitchen appliances, granite countertops, sink and recessed lighting. There's a pantry and seperate laundry room. Upgrades also include ceiling fans in all the bedrooms, Plantation shutters throughout. The master bath has a double sink vanity with a new custom tile countertop and sinks A much sought after feature is the separate living room and family room with a wood burning stove for those chilly winter nights. The floor plan allows for large family gatherings for all your guests. The property has a main driveway to the garage that circles back to the road and a circular driveway that goes around the back of the house to RV PARKING WITH ALL THE HOOKUPS. The property has a newer huge 12' by 20' custom built storage shed/workshop. The Master Bedroom has two walk-in closets and a sliding door going out to the fenced off Hot Tub area and yard. The guest bedrooms are ample in size, one has a walk-in closet. The concrete patio and the yard are perfect for large gatherings, the yards are so peaceful looking there's even a fenced off garden area to keep the deer out.Washer, dryer, fridge, hot tub, riding mower are negotiable.
